* {{ill|Tamaruhime|ja|多満留姫|1=Tamatsuhime|12=draft}} * {{ill|Takeminakata no Kami|ja|建御名方神|12=draft}} * {{ill|List of People Before the Asuka Period|ja|飛鳥時代以前の人物一覧|12=draft}}
