Yatsuakata Sukune no Kami is the child of {{ill|Izuhayao no Mikoto|ja|出早雄命|1=Izuhayao-no-Mikoto|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Izuhayao no Mikoto|13=User:Immanuelle/Izuhayao-no-Mikoto|qq=}}
, who is himself the son of {{ill|Takeminakata|lt=Takeminakata|lt=Takeminakata no Kami|ja|建御名方神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeminakata no Kami|qq=}} and {{ill|Yasakatome|lt=Yasakatome|lt=Yasakatome no Kami|ja|八坂刀売神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yasakatome no Kami|qq=}}. Yatsuakata's mother may have been {{ill|Tamaru-hime|ja|多満留姫|1=Tamaru-hime|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tamaru-hime|13=User:Immanuelle/Tamaru-hime|qq=}}. He had siblings, including {{ill|Kamohagami|ja|可毛羽神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kamohagami|qq=}}, {{ill|Wakakihime|ja|若木比売神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wakakihime|qq=}}, {{ill|Kusanaihime|ja|草奈井比売神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kusanaihime|qq=}}, {{ill|Izuhayahime|ja|伊津早姫神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Izuhayahime|qq=}}, as well as {{ill|Okata no Kami|ja|大縣神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Okata no Kami|qq=}}, {{ill|Uchiakata no Kami|ja|内安賀多神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Uchiakata no Kami|qq=}}, and {{ill|Sotakata no Kami|ja|外安賀多神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sotakata no Kami|qq=}}. Some genealogies also include {{ill|Aizu-hime-no-Kami|ja|会津比売神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Aizuhime no Kami|qq=}}, described as either a sibling or offspring of Yatsuakata.{{Sfn|Jinosuke|1912|p=73}}

