== Genealogy == [[File:Moriya Family Tree - 守矢氏系図.png|thumb|center|200px|Genealogy of the first five generations of the {{ill|Moriya clan|ja|守矢氏|1=Moriya clan|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Moriya clan|13=User:Immanuelle/Moriya clan|qq=}}]]
Yatsuakata Sukune no Kami is the child of {{ill|Izuhayao no Mikoto|ja|出早雄命|1=Izuhayao-no-Mikoto|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Izuhayao no Mikoto|13=User:Immanuelle/Izuhayao-no-Mikoto|qq=}} , who is himself the son of [[:en:Takeminakata|Takeminakata]] and [[:en:Yasakatome|Yasakatome no Kami]]. Yatsuakata's mother may have been {{ill|Tamaru-hime|ja|多満留姫|1=Tamaru-hime|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tamaru-hime|13=User:Immanuelle/Tamaru-hime|qq=}}. He had siblings, including {{ill|Kamohagami|ja|可毛羽神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kamohagami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, {{ill|Wakakihime|ja|若木比売神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wakakihime|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, {{ill|Kusanaihime|ja|草奈井比売神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kusanaihime|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, {{ill|Izuhayahime|ja|伊津早姫神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Izuhayahime|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, as well as {{ill|Okata no Kami|ja|大縣神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Okata no Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, {{ill|Uchiakata no Kami|ja|内安賀多神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Uchiakata no Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, and {{ill|Sotakata no Kami|ja|外安賀多神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sotakata no Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}. Some genealogies also include {{ill|Aizu-hime-no-Kami|ja|会津比売神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Aizuhime no Kami|qq=}}, described as either a sibling or offspring of Yatsuakata.{{Sfn|Jinosuke|1912|p=73}}
